<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7437145>
    dc:description "Figure 23 Phylogenetic results. (A) Strict consensus of the 1,500 MPTs found in the second iteration; (B) simplified strict consensus of the 1,620 MPTs found in the first iteration. (C) Alternative arrangements for the Serra da Galga Specimens and G. faustoi on Iteration I. Nodes: 1, Titanosauriformes; 2, Somphospondylii; 3, Titanosauria; 4, Colossosauria; 5, Rinconsauria; 6, Aeolosaurini. Full-size DOI: 10.7717/peerj.14333/fig-23" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7437145/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

